# WoW Addon Project Guide

## Project Overview

We are developing a World of Warcraft addon for the 1.12 client (Classic/Vanilla) using Lua 5.0. This project emphasizes clean, readable code that follows industry best practices.

## Technical Specifications

- **Target Client**: World of Warcraft 1.12 (Classic/Vanilla)
- **Programming Language**: Lua 5.0
- **License**: Open Source
